        "title": "Lesson Introduction: Environmental Awareness and Passive Voice",
        "description": "Introduce the theme of environmental protection from Lesson 143 and the grammatical focus on the passive voice (present perfect and future) from Lesson 144. Briefly explain how these two lessons complement each other."
